longBusinessSummary: Gaming Corps AB (publ) operates as a game development company. The company engages in developing games within iGAMING business areas. It develops games in casino slots, plinko games, multiplier games, smash4cash games, table games, and mine games category. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Uppsala, Sweden.
